50|$|Total Information Awareness (TIA) was {{a program}} of the United States Information Awareness Office that began during the 2003 fiscal year. It {{operated}} under this title from February until May 2003, before being renamed as the <b>Terrorism</b> <b>Information</b> <b>Awareness.</b>|$|E
